{
  "texts": [
    "Another approach involves utilizing ChatGPT for generating feedback.",
    "To build upon the research conducted by Taghipour and Ng (2016) in incorporating trait information, Hussein et al. (2020) proposed a model that not only predicts the overall score but also provides trait-specific scores.",
    "This approach aims to enhance the performance of the overall score while enabling adaptive feedback based on specific traits.",
    "However, a significant challenge arises due to the limited availability of annotated datasets that include trait information.",
    "Woods et al. (2017) utilizes ordinal logistic regression model for essay scoring which attains the state-of-the-art performance on essays with low range of scores while keeping features that are useful for sentence influence estimation task."
  ]
}